Comment: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你剛才親眼看見的是什麼?
Comment: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,殺害你同伴的 不就是那女人嗎?
Comment: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道你還不肯相信?
Comment: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,吵死了
Comment: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我已經在做了!
Comment: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮她是女巨人?
Comment: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼...
Comment: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼你會這麼認為? 阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,女巨人在一開始的時候就知道艾連的長相
Comment: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,連只有同期生才知道的艾連綽號
Comment: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,「趕著去投胎的傢伙」都有反應
Comment: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,最重要的原因是
Comment: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我認為殺死實驗體索尼跟賓的
Comment: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是亞妮
Comment: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼你會知道?
Comment: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要殺害那兩名巨人需要高超的技術
Comment: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,勢必得利用自己已經用慣了的立體機動裝置
Comment: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以說檢查裝備的那個時候
Comment: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:32.37,Default,Q,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮沒有被抓到啊
Comment: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個時候...
Comment: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮所呈交上去的是馬可的物品
Comment: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以才逃過了追查
Comment: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在說什麼?
Comment: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼會提到馬可?
Comment: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也不知道
Comment: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會不會是你看錯
Comment: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不
Comment: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個我確實有印象...
Comment: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 小鬼
Comment: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個我已經知道了
Comment: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你還有其他證據嗎?
Comment: 0,0:09:58.94,0:09:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有
Comment: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我認為亞妮的臉跟女巨人長得很像
Comment: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,蛤? 妳在說什麼啊
Comment: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就只是因為這點程度的證據...
Comment: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說你們沒根據就要動手囉
Comment: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有根據...
Comment: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是怎樣
Comment: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼要動手?
Comment: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果不是亞妮的話你們該怎麼辦?
Comment: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果不是亞妮的話
Comment: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就只是證明了她的清白
Comment: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那樣的話我也覺得很對不起亞妮
Comment: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是...
Comment: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為這樣而什麼都不做的話
Comment: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連你將會成為中央那群人的犧牲品
Comment: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要懷疑亞妮這實在太奇怪了
Comment: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,剛才聽到是亞妮
Comment: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道你都沒想起什麼嗎?
Comment: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,既然你曾經跟女巨人以格鬥技交手過
Comment: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道沒看到她使出亞妮獨有的技巧嗎?
Comment: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你應該很清楚吧?
Comment: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,其實女巨人
Comment: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是亞妮
Comment: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼
Comment: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你就非打不可了吧?
Comment: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還是說...
Comment: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有什麼特殊的情感讓你猶豫了?
Comment: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我想到作戰策略了
Comment: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我跟米卡莎同時從那個洞跟原本的出口離開
Comment: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如此一來亞妮就只能對付其中一個
Comment: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連你就趁機從亞妮不在的方向逃走!
Comment: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等等!
Comment: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣的話不就等於你們有一個會死嗎?
Comment: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但待在這裡我們三個都會死
Comment: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎 就定位吧
Comment: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,知道了
Comment: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我負責前面
Comment: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼...
Comment: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼你們能夠跟她戰鬥啊?
Comment: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼!!
Comment: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這也沒辦法啊
Comment: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這世界就是如此殘酷
Comment: 0,0:12:58.45,0:12:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,CM
Comment: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮
Comment: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我絕對不會讓妳奪走艾連的!
Comment: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我現在就來救你
Comment: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把手伸給我
Comment: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別讓女巨人逃了!
Comment: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我絕對不讓妳往這外面跑
Comment: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底發生了什麼事...
Comment: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,護衛班這裡可以了
Comment: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,過去看看狀況!
Comment: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,了解了
Comment: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,奇怪
Comment: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,剛剛的爆炸聲也是
Comment: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,奈爾
Comment: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,立刻派出所有士兵吧
Comment: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在應該視為巨人已經出現了
Comment: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在說什麼?
Comment: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這裡可是席納之牆欸!
Comment: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人怎麼可能會出現!
Comment: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等一下 不要動葉卡
Comment: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,變裝遊戲到此結束!
Comment: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別再用那個名字叫我 你這王八蛋!
Comment: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,團長我也要去
Comment: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,裝備去跟四班那邊拿
Comment: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,了解了
Comment: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有氣勢是很好啦
Comment: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別給我找死喔
Comment: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好
Comment: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾爾文這到底在做什麼...
Comment: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,團長 接著這個
Comment: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,辛苦了
Comment: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不會!
Comment: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 艾爾文!
Comment: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能動的人全部向前進
Comment: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,去跟女巨人捕捉班會合
Comment: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾爾文 給我等等!
Comment: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你現在在做的事情
Comment: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明顯是對王政的叛逆行為
Comment: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,奈爾
Comment: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你的腦漿是稀到爆是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你似乎連發生了什麼都不知道
Comment: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,卸下裝備 艾爾文!
Comment: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是巨人 巨人來了!
Comment: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:39.98,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼會在這裡!?
Comment: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂...那個是巨人...
Comment: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是為什麼...
Comment: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,閃開
Comment: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是夠了 過得太爽
Comment: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我本來應該是在那邊的是嗎...
Comment: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我到底是怎麼了啊
Comment: 0,0:15:59.15,0:15:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該死
Comment: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要想要打倒她 我們只要纏住她就好了!
Comment: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不行了 立體機動裝置的活動太僵硬了
Comment: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我會讓妳吃不完兜著走!
Comment: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快回應我
Comment: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 你在做什麼啊!
Comment: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰
Comment: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連在這個下面
Comment: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,蛤? 依照計畫他應該變成巨人才對吧
Comment: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他沒有辦到
Comment: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我想是因為女巨人的真身是亞妮才對他造成了影響
Comment: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮?
Comment: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總之要快點把他救出來
Comment: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰快來幫我
Comment: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有辦到?
Comment: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連 你在開什麼玩笑
Comment: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我應該說過總有一天會需要靠你
Comment: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,竟然要對你這種人
Comment: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個世界以及全部人類
Comment: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,甚至連自己的生命都得要託付於你
Comment: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們的回報就是這樣嗎!
Comment: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,馬可...馬可他...
Comment: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該死
Comment: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連...
Comment: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不行了
Comment: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要先處理一下那個傢伙才行
Comment: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我曾被約翰說過一句話
Comment: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對於無法捨棄任何東西的人
Comment: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就無法改變任何事情
Comment: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果真要隱藏自己是怪物的話
Comment: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼他連人性都能捨去
Comment: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我想亞妮 她一定做得到
Comment: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然不知道她是為了什麼
Comment: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是...
Comment: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能夠捨棄的人才能夠贏得勝利
Comment: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮!
Comment: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳這次不把我給殺掉的話
Comment: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,之後妳想逞強不認輸都很難喔!
Comment: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏這裡!
Comment: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,了解!
Comment: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嘿嘿嘿嘿 要來了
Comment: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要來了
Comment: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:48.60,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,分隊長你的眼睛....
Comment: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,晃得很嚴重...
Comment: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,很好
Comment: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我還以為第三階段作戰會沒有出場的機會
Comment: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真不愧是艾爾文團長
Comment: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,接下來...
Comment: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,乖小孩 妳要乖乖的
Comment: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這裡可不像之前一樣
Comment: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可叫不出會把妳吃光的巨人
Comment: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是沒關係的
Comment: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我會替他們把妳給吃了
Comment: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把妳藏住的那些情報給吃了
Comment: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她掙脫了!?
Comment: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,果然陷阱的數量不夠嗎
Comment: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別讓她逃了!快追!
Comment: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對於無法捨棄任何東西的人
Comment: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就無法改變任何事物
Comment: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這我知道
Comment: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就是在那...
Comment: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,被夥伴...
Comment: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,被夥伴之間的情感所困才會失敗的
Comment: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點想起來
Comment: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我要驅逐你們...
Comment: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不...
Comment: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是殺光你們!
Comment: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我沒有時間去想是不是正確的
Comment: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總之給我動起來
Comment: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別給我說大話後就給我結束
Comment: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯
Comment: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這世界是殘酷的
Comment: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次是怎樣!
Comment: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連...
Comment: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:23:53.25,0:23:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從這世上...
Comment: 0,0:23:54.31,0:23:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一隻不留地將巨人給驅逐殆盡
Comment: 0,0:23:58.11,0:23:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那天...
Comment: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓幼小的艾連如此發誓的憤怒
Comment: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,使他去追趕著獵物
Comment: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,並叫他去破壞這整個世界
