Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏 還好我是你心目中的好人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你基本上算是賭贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的賭注... 才正要開始呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們找到了疑似是女巨人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文那群人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又給我搞這招
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣憲兵團豈不是就會先來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在應該是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}超大型的屎一直拉不出來而感到困擾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你今天話還滿多的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我本來就很會說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我在那個時候....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果沒有做錯選擇的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就不會這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不是說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}結果是沒有人能料到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抱歉 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒關係...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們幾個...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們找到了疑似是女巨人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次要確實地把她給捕捉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}作戰在後天執行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}地點是我們被召回到王都的途中會通過的史托黑斯區
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這會是最後的一次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}錯過了這次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連就會被交付給王都
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}追趕企圖破壞城牆的那些傢伙們也會變得很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}簡單來說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類滅亡的危機就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們將在這次作戰中賭上一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}作戰計畫的內容是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}通過史托黑斯區的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連將作為誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將目標逼入這個地下隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把她逼到最深處後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以大小跟行動範圍來看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算目標變成了巨人 也有可能封住她的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是萬一她在這之前變成巨人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就會變成要麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}最重要的目標已經確認是在史托黑斯區裡面了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}目標隸屬於憲兵團
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}憲兵團?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}推論出這件事情的是阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}推測女巨人也是殺害了之前所活捉兩名巨人的兇手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也很可能是你們104期訓練軍團的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等... 請等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說...104期...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被推斷為女巨人的那位女性的名字是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮．雷恩哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}糟...糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}該死 那個戒指...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}果然我的謊言在一開始就被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也早就被料到有人事先埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}其實應該還有其他方法才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}反省等等再跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}先告訴我們現在應該做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之先跟三班會合回到地面上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後就進行第二階段作戰的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:05:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跟亞妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跟女巨人戰鬥!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而艾連你則依照計畫變成巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}協助我們將她抓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是3班!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}第一階段的捕捉失敗了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}失敗了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請轉成執行第二階段作戰!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被踩穿了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我得去救他!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 你退後!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 米卡莎!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}女巨人那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道艾連死了也沒關係嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她在賭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她賭艾連不會死所以才大膽踩出一個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然很亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但也表示她很難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮她...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}拚了命想把艾連搶過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}退路被封了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算使用立體機動快速地逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她也會在那一瞬間出手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}話雖如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但一直躲在這裡也不知道什麼時候會被她踩爛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我來想點辦法吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就像那個時候阻擋大砲一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們都靠過來!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要開始囉!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要離開我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又來了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}竟然在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}該死 有夠痛!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}缺乏確切的目的就無法變成巨人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再試著想像一次!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}強烈點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我在試了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你是不是還在猶豫要不要跟亞妮交戰?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難不成到了現在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你還認為亞妮是女巨人這件事情只是我們想太多嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你剛才親眼看見的是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}殺害你同伴的 不就是那女人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道你還不肯相信?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我已經在做了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮她是女巨人?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼你會這麼認為? 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}女巨人在一開始的時候就知道艾連的長相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}連只有同期生才知道的艾連綽號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}「趕著去投胎的傢伙」都有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}最重要的原因是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我認為殺死實驗體索尼跟賓的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是亞妮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼你會知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要殺害那兩名巨人需要高超的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}勢必得利用自己已經用慣了的立體機動裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以說檢查裝備的那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:32.37,Default,Q,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮沒有被抓到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮所呈交上去的是馬可的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以才逃過了追查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼會提到馬可?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會不會是你看錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個我確實有印象...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你還有其他證據嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:09:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我認為亞妮的臉跟女巨人長得很像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}蛤? 妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就只是因為這點程度的證據...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也就是說你們沒根據就要動手囉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有根據...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼要動手?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果不是亞妮的話你們該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果不是亞妮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就只是證明了她的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那樣的話我也覺得很對不起亞妮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為這樣而什麼都不做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連你將會成為中央那群人的犧牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要懷疑亞妮這實在太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剛才聽到是亞妮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道你都沒想起什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}既然你曾經跟女巨人以格鬥技交手過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道沒看到她使出亞妮獨有的技巧嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你應該很清楚吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}其實女巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是亞妮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你就非打不可了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有什麼特殊的情感讓你猶豫了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想到作戰策略了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我跟米卡莎同時從那個洞跟原本的出口離開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如此一來亞妮就只能對付其中一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連你就趁機從亞妮不在的方向逃走!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣的話不就等於你們有一個會死嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但待在這裡我們三個都會死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎 就定位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我負責前面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼你們能夠跟她戰鬥啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這世界就是如此殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:12:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我絕對不會讓妳奪走艾連的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我現在就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把手伸給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別讓女巨人逃了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我絕對不讓妳往這外面跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底發生了什麼事...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}護衛班這裡可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}過去看看狀況!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剛剛的爆炸聲也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}奈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}立刻派出所有士兵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在應該視為巨人已經出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這裡可是席納之牆欸!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人怎麼可能會出現!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等一下 不要動葉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}變裝遊戲到此結束!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別再用那個名字叫我 你這王八蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}團長我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}裝備去跟四班那邊拿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有氣勢是很好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別給我找死喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文這到底在做什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}團長 接著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不會!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 艾爾文!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}能動的人全部向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}去跟女巨人捕捉班會合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文 給我等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你現在在做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明顯是對王政的叛逆行為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}奈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你的腦漿是稀到爆是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你似乎連發生了什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}卸下裝備 艾爾文!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是巨人 巨人來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:39.98,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼會在這裡!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂...那個是巨人...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是夠了 過得太爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我本來應該是在那邊的是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我到底是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:15:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}該死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要想要打倒她 我們只要纏住她就好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不行了 立體機動裝置的活動太僵硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我會讓妳吃不完兜著走!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快回應我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 你在做什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連在這個下面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}蛤? 依照計畫他應該變成巨人才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他沒有辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想是因為女巨人的真身是亞妮才對他造成了影響
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之要快點把他救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰快來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有辦到?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 你在開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我應該說過總有一天會需要靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}竟然要對你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個世界以及全部人類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}甚至連自己的生命都得要託付於你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們的回報就是這樣嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}馬可...馬可他...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}該死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要先處理一下那個傢伙才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我曾被約翰說過一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對於無法捨棄任何東西的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就無法改變任何事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果真要隱藏自己是怪物的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那麼他連人性都能捨去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想亞妮 她一定做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然不知道她是為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}能夠捨棄的人才能夠贏得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亞妮!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳這次不把我給殺掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}之後妳想逞強不認輸都很難喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏這裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嘿嘿嘿嘿 要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:48.60,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}分隊長你的眼睛....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}晃得很嚴重...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我還以為第三階段作戰會沒有出場的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真不愧是艾爾文團長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}接下來...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}乖小孩 妳要乖乖的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這裡可不像之前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可叫不出會把妳吃光的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我會替他們把妳給吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把妳藏住的那些情報給吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她掙脫了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}果然陷阱的數量不夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別讓她逃了!快追!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對於無法捨棄任何東西的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就無法改變任何事物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我就是在那...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被夥伴...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被夥伴之間的情感所困才會失敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要驅逐你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是殺光你們!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒有時間去想是不是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之給我動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別給我說大話後就給我結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這世界是殘酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次是怎樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.25,0:23:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從這世上...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.31,0:23:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一隻不留地將巨人給驅逐殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:23:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那天...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓幼小的艾連如此發誓的憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}使他去追趕著獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}並叫他去破壞這整個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
